    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true collector-grade masterpiece in showroom condition. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like clarity enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections to be found. Every body panel aligns perfectly, and the trim remains factory-supple. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule, retaining its original new-car scent with leather surfaces that are soft, matte, and entirely free of bolster wear or creasing. All electronics, switches, and displays function with tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is detailed to a concours standard, reflecting a meticulous maintenance history performed exclusively by certified technicians. This vehicle has been stored in a climate-controlled environment, never driven in inclement weather, and comes complete with a comprehensive service binder, all original keys, and the window sticker. It drives with the tightness and responsiveness of a vehicle that just rolled off the assembly line.",
